  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个序列图，展示页面渲染的完整流程。最左边是page节点，它渲染比较慢，而且是jay-html类型的。然后中间是page component，右边是child components。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "page",
        "page component",
        "child components"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，page节点我标注为\"slowly rendered\"和\"jay-html\"。那page component和child components之间是什么关系？是page component先激活，然后再和page交互吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "page",
        "page component",
        "child components",
        "activate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，流程是这样的：server先把props和app settings传给page component，这时候激活page component。这里要加个注释，说明它加载快且数据会变。然后page component把vs和client props回传给page。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "page component",
        "page",
        "server props",
        "app settings",
        "vs",
        "client props",
        "activate",
        "Note"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我添加了page component的生命周期，包括激活、server props传入、注释\"load fast changing data\"，然后deactivate。接下来page被激活后，需要做什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "page component",
        "page",
        "activate",
        "deactivate",
        "Note"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "page激活后，要把vs映射到child components的props上，这个也加个注释在page左边。然后page把props和app settings传给child components，激活child。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "page",
        "child components",
        "vs",
        "props",
        "app settings",
        "activate",
        "Note"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，page到child components的消息，加上注释\"map vs to child components props\"。child激活后也需要同样的注释说明加载快吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "page",
        "child components",
        "Note",
        "activate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，child右边也加\"load fast changing data\"。然后child把vs和client props回传给page，deactivate child，再激活page做最后的html渲染。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "child components",
        "page",
        "vs",
        "client props",
        "deactivate",
        "activate",
        "html"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。最后page的注释是\"rendering html send to client\"，然后deactivate。整个流程：page component和child components都是快速加载的可变数据节点，page负责协调映射和最终html输出。",
      "elements_involved": [
